{
  "text": "What was the attitude just prior to harvest of those harvestable entities of Ra with respect to those who were obviously unharvestable. I am raw. Those of us which had the gift of holarity, a felt deep compassion for those who seemed to dwell in a darkness. This description is a most apt as ours was a harshly bright planet in the aphysical sense. However, those upon the positive path have the comfort of companions, and we of Ara spent a great deal of our attention upon the possibilities of achieving a spiritual or metaphysical adepthood or work in indigo array through the means of relationships with others. Consequently, the compassion for those in a darkness was balanced by the appreciation of the light.",
